class DataReader():
    def __init__(self):
        self.label = ["paper", "rock", "scissors"]

        self.train_X = []
        self.train_Y = []
        self.test_X = []
        self.test_Y = []

        self.read_images()

    def read_images(self):
        data = []
        root = os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath("__file__"))
        print("Reading Data...")
        classes = ["paper", "rock", "scissors"]
        for i, cls in enumerate(classes):
            print("Opening " + cls + "/")
            for el in os.listdir(root + "/" + cls):
                img = Image.open(root + "/" + cls + "/" + el)
                data.append((np.asarray(img), i))
                img.close()

        random.shuffle(data)

        for i in range(len(data)):
            if i < 0.8*len(data):
                self.train_X.append(data[i][0])
                self.train_Y.append(data[i][1])
            else:
                self.test_X.append(data[i][0])
                self.test_Y.append(data[i][1])

        # 이미지 정규화
        self.train_X = np.asarray(self.train_X) / 255.0
        self.train_Y = np.asarray(self.train_Y)
        self.test_X = np.asarray(self.test_X) / 255.0
        self.test_Y = np.asarray(self.test_Y)

        # 데이터 읽기가 완료되었습니다.
        # 읽어온 데이터의 정보를 출력합니다.
        print("\n\nData Read Done!")
        print("Training X Size : " + str(self.train_X.shape))
        print("Training Y Size : " + str(self.train_Y.shape))
        print("Test X Size : " + str(self.test_X.shape))
        print("Test Y Size : " + str(self.test_Y.shape) + '\n\n')

    def show_processed_images(self):
        """ 훈련 데이터에서 샘플 이미지를 표시하는 함수 (리스트 변환 적용) """
        plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))
        num_images = min(25, len(self.train_X))  # 최대 25개까지만 표시

        # ✅ train_Y를 리스트로 변환 (원-핫 인코딩 → 클래스 인덱스 리스트)
        train_labels = np.argmax(self.train_Y, axis=1).tolist()

        for i in range(num_images):
            plt.subplot(5, 5, i + 1)
            plt.xticks([])
            plt.yticks([])
            plt.grid(False)
            plt.imshow(self.train_X[i])  # ✅ 컬러 이미지 그대로 표시
            plt.xlabel(self.label[train_labels[i]])  # ✅ 클래스 인덱스 리스트 사용

        plt.tight_layout()
        plt.show()

    def show_prediction_results(self, model):
        """ 모델 예측 결과를 시각화하는 함수 (리스트 변환 적용) """
        plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
        predictions = model.predict(self.test_X[:20])  # 첫 20개 샘플 예측
        predicted_labels = np.argmax(predictions, axis=1).tolist()  # ✅ 리스트 변환
        
        # ✅ test_Y를 리스트로 변환 (원-핫 인코딩 → 클래스 인덱스 리스트)
        actual_labels = np.argmax(self.test_Y[:20], axis=1).tolist()

        for i in range(len(predicted_labels)):
            plt.subplot(4, 5, i + 1)
            plt.xticks([])
            plt.yticks([])
            plt.grid(False)
            plt.imshow(self.test_X[i])  # ✅ 컬러 이미지 그대로 표시
            
            predicted = self.label[predicted_labels[i]]  # 예측된 클래스
            actual = self.label[actual_labels[i]]  # 실제 클래스
            color = "green" if predicted == actual else "red"  # 정답 여부에 따른 색상

            plt.xlabel(f'예측: {predicted}\n실제: {actual}', color=color)

        plt.tight_layout()
        plt.show()



def draw_graph(history):
    train_history = history.history["loss"]
    validation_history = history.history["val_loss"]
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))
    plt.title("Loss History")
    plt.xlabel("EPOCH")
    plt.ylabel("LOSS Function")
    plt.plot(train_history, "red")
    plt.plot(validation_history, 'blue')
    fig.savefig("train_history.png")

    train_history = history.history["accuracy"]
    validation_history = history.history["val_accuracy"]
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))
    plt.title("Accuracy History")
    plt.xlabel("EPOCH")
    plt.ylabel("Accuracy")
    plt.plot(train_history, "red")
    plt.plot(validation_history, 'blue')
    fig.savefig("accuracy_history.png")
In [40]:
dr = DataReader()
# One-hot encoding
dr.train_Y = to_categorical(dr.train_Y, num_classes=3)
dr.test_Y = to_categorical(dr.test_Y, num_classes=3)
model = keras.Sequential([
    keras.layers.Conv2D(16, (3, 3), activation="relu"),
    keras.layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)),
    keras.layers.Conv2D(32, (3, 3), activation='relu'),
    keras.layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)),
    keras.layers.Conv2D(64, (3, 3), activation='relu'),
    keras.layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)),
    keras.layers.Conv2D(64, (3, 3), activation='relu'),
    keras.layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)),
    keras.layers.Conv2D(64, (3, 3), activation='relu'),
    keras.layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)),
    keras.layers.Flatten(),
    keras.layers.Dense(128, activation='relu'),
    keras.layers.Dense(3, activation='softmax')  # 3개 클래스 분류
])

model.compile(optimizer='adam', metrics=['accuracy'],
              loss='categorical_crossentropy')

print("\n\n************ TRAINING START ************ ")
early_stop = keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(monitor='val_loss', patience=10)
history = model.fit(dr.train_X, dr.train_Y, epochs=30,
                    validation_data=(dr.test_X, dr.test_Y),
                    callbacks=[early_stop])

draw_graph(history)
